2003-08-06 15:03  castaglia

	* ChangeLog, Make.rules.in, NEWS, README.IPv6, config.h.in,
	configure.in, contrib/mod_ifsession.c, contrib/mod_radius.c,
	contrib/mod_ratio.c, contrib/mod_rewrite.c, contrib/mod_sql.c,
