	* include/options.h: 
	Increase default PR_TUNABLE_LOGIN_MAX size (and don't use
	_POSIX_LOGIN_NAME_MAX, even if it is defined).	Should fix
	Bug#2079.

2003-06-04 10:03  castaglia

	* configure: 
	Updating configure.

