2003-01-02 18:16  jwm

	* README.linux-privs, configure.in, contrib/mod_linuxprivs.c,
	contrib/mod_linuxprivs.html, lib/libcap/.cvsignore,
	lib/libcap/Makefile, lib/libcap/_makenames.c,
