2002-05-10 13:14  castaglia

	* NEWS: 
	
	Bug#1580 - RPM can't be built by non-root user

2002-05-10 13:08  castaglia

	* contrib/dist/rpm/proftpd.spec.in: 
	
	Bug#1580 - RPM can't be built by non-root user

